Hagiwara Electric to dissolve subsidiary












Monday, 31 Jul 2017 04:18am EDT July 31(Reuters) - Hagiwara Electric Co Ltd <7467.T>:Says it plans to dissolve a wholly owned subsidiary, which is engaged in electronic devices sales business in China .Effective date March 31, 2018. 



