Light source box



Our products "light source box", adjust the white balance the camera, the imager sensors, cameras Automotive (for safe driving), such as a camera for image processing, the amount of light, inspection, involving the use of our wide range of standard "light source box" as a pattern for calibration We. Please contact us special order, and built-in support.
Light source box


Category　page

One point light source box
One point light source that outputs a steady luminance with high uniformity.
For a compact, the flexibility of the place is high.
Light source box having some luminance points
Light source switching the brightness of the point from 4 to 8.
Best way to use a fixed luminance.
Light source box with feedback of quantity of light
To monitor the luminance to compensate.
Every time there is no need to adjust the luminance.
Light source box using xenon lamp
Light source using a xenon.
Approximation to the spectrum of natural daylight.
Light source box with wide range of luminance
Output in any luminance from low luminance to high luminance.
Best way to use a wide range of luminance.


Light source box with LED light
Light source using a LED.
Best way to use a "RGB" LED and white LED.
Light source box for calibration of luminance meter
A highly stable luminance and high uniformity light source .
The calibration of luminance meter, compact light source optimal.
Light source box using integrating sphere
Light source using an integrating sphere.
Luminance high uniformity light source.
Light source box changing luminance by manual
Light source luminance can be adjusted manually steplessly.
Light source manual adjustment, cheaper version.
Light source box with some color temperature
Light source color temperature can be switched.
Best way to use multiple color temperature.



Viewer light source



4:3 and 16:9, inspection of a variety of size, has been held by a light source such as the evaluation chart viewer for devices up to A1 ~ A4 size. Resolving power, function AF, available also target chart of backscattering.
Viewer light source


Category　page

Chart system
Resolving power, function AF, the measurement of the distance measurement function.


Viewer light source
Luminance high uniformity the various"viewer" series.



Lens tester



Adjustment is done accurately in a single lens, the lens unit measurement or inspection, such as cameras and digital cameras and video camera.
Lens tester


Category page

Measurement instrument involved in the lens
Measuring instrument related to the lens.Focal length, such as spherical aberration and FNo.etc.



Shutter tester



The inspection camera precisely, digital camera, portable camera, the measurement of fast shutter speed.Experience in development and production line for many years, is abundant.
